How to add new themes to installation-images
============================================

1. Add a new branch to the switch()-like statement in lib/ReadConfig.pm
   (search for 'theme').

2. If there is a new bootsplash-theme-* package:

   - add the bootsplash-theme-* package to data/base/base.file_list
   - at the end of data/base/base.file_list, create the boot splash

